<title>USA: Wasserstein Perella hires senior adviser.</title>
<headline>Wasserstein Perella hires senior adviser.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-02-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Investment banking firm Wasserstein Perella Group Inc said it has hired former Thomson SA and Thomson-CSF chairman and chief executive officer Alain Gomez as a senior adviser based in Paris.</p>
<p>Prior to his 14 years at Thomson, the 58-year-old Gomez was vice president in charge of the packaging group at Saint-Gobain.</p>
